📅 Time Table / Daily Planner (C Language)

📌 Overview

This is a simple Time Table / Daily Planner built using the C programming language.
It helps users organize their daily schedule by storing and viewing tasks for different time slots.

---

🚀 Features

- ➕ Add schedule/task
- 📋 View full timetable
- ⏰ Assign time slots to tasks
- 🔁 Menu-driven interface

---

🛠️ Technologies Used

- C Programming Language
- Standard Libraries ("stdio.h", "string.h")

---

💡 Example Output

--- TIME TABLE ---
1. Add Task
2. View Time Table
3. Exit

Enter choice: 1
Enter time (e.g., 10AM): 10AM
Enter task: Study C Programming
Task added!

---

🧠 Concepts Used

- Arrays (for storing tasks)
- Strings ("fgets", "strcmp")
- Loops ("while")
- Conditional statements ("switch", "if-else")

